Title: 核心对象/函数说明
Describe: SDK、CLI、ACP 和 partner 包中的关键对象职责。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S03_CORE_OBJECTS - SDK 核心对象

[Description]
SDK 的中心是 `create_deep_agent`，它把模型解析、profile、tools、backend、subagents、middleware、prompt 和 state schema 装配成一个 `CompiledStateGraph`。

[UML]
@startuml
class "DeepAgentState" as DeepAgentState {
  messages: DeltaChannel
}
class "create_deep_agent" as CreateDeepAgent {
  model
  tools
  subagents
  skills
  memory
  permissions
  backend
  interrupt_on
}
class "FilesystemMiddleware" as FSM
class "SubAgentMiddleware" as SAM
class "AsyncSubAgentMiddleware" as ASAM
class "MemoryMiddleware" as MM
class "HarnessProfile" as HP
class "StateBackend" as SB
CreateDeepAgent --> HP : resolve profile
CreateDeepAgent --> SB : default backend
CreateDeepAgent --> FSM : file tools and permissions
CreateDeepAgent --> SAM : task tool
CreateDeepAgent --> ASAM : remote tasks
CreateDeepAgent --> MM : memory sources
CreateDeepAgent --> DeepAgentState : default schema
@enduml

[Detail]
`DeepAgentState` 在 `graph.py:63-66` 为 `messages` 使用 `DeltaChannel`，避免 checkpoint 随历史消息 O(N²) 增长。`create_deep_agent` 的签名在 `graph.py:217-237`，公开参数覆盖 model、tools、middleware、subagents、skills、memory、permissions、backend、HITL、structured output、schema、checkpointer、store、cache 等。`_REQUIRED_MIDDLEWARE` 在 `graph.py:187-201` 把 `FilesystemMiddleware` 与 `SubAgentMiddleware` 标为不能被 profile 排除的脚手架能力。箭头表示装配关系，不表示继承。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
部署 CLI 对象

[Description]
部署 CLI 以 `Project` dataclass 表示本地 managed-agent 项目，以 payload builder 生成远端 API 请求和目录 commit delta。

[UML]
@startuml
class "Project" as Project {
  root
  agent_id
  name
  model
  system_prompt
  tools
  skills
  subagents
}
class "Skill" as Skill {
  name
  description
  instructions
  files
}
class "Subagent" as Subagent {
  name
  model_id
  instructions
  tools
  extra_files
}
class "payload.py" as Payload
class "ApiClient" as ApiClient
Project *-- Skill
Project *-- Subagent
Payload --> Project : build_payload
Payload --> Project : build_directory_files
Payload --> ApiClient : request bodies
@enduml

[Detail]
`Project`、`Skill`、`Subagent` 位于 `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/deploy/project.py:115-157`。`Project.load` 在 `project.py:159-188` 读取 `agent.json`、`AGENTS.md`、`tools.json`、skills 和 subagents。`payload.py:20-43` 生成 create payload，`payload.py:46-61` 生成 metadata patch payload，`payload.py:64-83` 生成远端 managed directory 文件集合，`payload.py:86-98` 计算远端目录 delta。CLI 命令使用这些对象，避免在 payload builder 内再次做 I/O。
